This is an extra sub-menu 'pulled down' by some sub-menu choices, usually
to provide additional details for that choice.  For instance, if you
selected PIE under the dessert sub-menu, this extra sub-menu allows you to
choose the variety of pie.  It operates like other menus and sub-menus.
Select an item with either the UP and DOWN arrow or by striking the keys
corresponding to the KEYS above (1, 2, 3, ... ).  When you have made your
choice, select it with the ENTER key.  You will then leave this menu.
